{"tid":2364072,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"路人甲變舞女　33D劉芷希為入行住劏房捱窮","createTime":"2021-01-12T16:25:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-12T17:02:15.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"67114cc2cc6f12d8f6578b62c7ac08ebdeb53eea","tid":2364072,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T16:25:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20210112/photo/bkn-20210112181542661-0112_00862_001_01p.jpg?20210112182816\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20210112%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20210112181542661-0112_00862_001_01p.jpg%3F20210112182816&h=37dbad2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n現年35歲、擁有33D導彈上圍的劉芷希模特兒出身，曾於2012年參選《中華小姐環球大賽》獲得亞軍、「完美體態小姐」及「最高貴氣質小姐」共三項殊榮，至2017年由馬來西亞來港轉戰珠寶小姐，成功奪冠後留港發展，並簽約無綫。惟其星途十分波折，她初來港發展時撞正模特兒公司倒閉，焗住劏房捱窮，豈料再遭人盜竊，被偷走現金及手袋損失近8萬港元，雙重打擊禍不單行。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20210112/photo/bkn-20210112155042535-0112_00862_001_04p.jpg?20210112210339\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20210112%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20210112155042535-0112_00862_001_04p.jpg%3F20210112210339&h=ae86cea8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"df6dbe982eb4ba17f137d8bec7fa60b8387acf28","tid":2364072,"uid":71632,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T16:27:42.000Z","msg":"假奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dd8a7a134948578457a1e04d4a1aba49c323d53","tid":2364072,"uid":182127,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T16:33:02.000Z","msg":"who.gif"},{"pid":"ace6253873bbb9bbc91c41ac673b98e53639e2d2","tid":2364072,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T16:44:38.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">並簽約無綫</span><br />\n<br />\n恭喜晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3382c70c2b053f44b90be5440a9c252